89class JsonStructHelper
90{
91 public:
92 static void MergeJson(QJsonObject &mergeTo, const QJsonObject &mergeIn)
93 {
94 for (const auto &key : mergeIn.keys())
95 mergeTo[key] = mergeIn.value(key);
96 }

98 template<typename T>
99 static void Deserialize(T &t, const QJsonValue &d)
100 {
101 if constexpr (std::is_enum_v<T>)
102 t = (T) d.toInt();
103 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonObject>)
104 t = d.toObject();
105 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonArray>)
106 t = d.toArray();
107 else
108 t.loadJson(d);
109 }

125 template<typename T>
126 static void Deserialize(QList<T> &t, const QJsonValue &d)
127 {
128 t.clear();
129 for (const auto &val : d.toArray())
130 {
131 T data;
132 Deserialize(data, val);
133 t.push_back(data);
134 }
135 }
136
137 template<typename TKey, typename TValue>
138 static void Deserialize(QMap<TKey, TValue> &t, const QJsonValue &d)
139 {
140 t.clear();
141 const auto &jsonObject = d.toObject();
142 TKey keyVal;
143 TValue valueVal;
144 for (const auto &key : jsonObject.keys())
145 {
146 Deserialize(keyVal, key);
147 Deserialize(valueVal, jsonObject.value(key));
148 t.insert(keyVal, valueVal);
149 }
150 }

154 template<typename T>
155 static QJsonValue Serialize(const T &t)
156 {
157 if constexpr (std::is_enum_v<T>)
158 return (int) t;
159 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonObject> || std::is_same_v<T, QJsonArray>)
160 return t;
161 else
162 return t.toJson();
163 }

193 template<typename TValue>
194 static QJsonValue Serialize(const QMap<QString, TValue> &t)
195 {
196 QJsonObject mapObject;
197 for (const auto &key : t.keys())
198 {
199 auto valueVal = Serialize(t.value(key));
200 mapObject.insert(key, valueVal);
201 }
202 return mapObject;
203 }
204
205 template<typename T>
206 static QJsonValue Serialize(const QList<T> &t)
207 {
208 QJsonArray listObject;
209 for (const auto &item : t)
210 {
211 listObject.push_back(Serialize(item));
212 }
213 return listObject;
214 }
